data.description: Retail buyers welcome.  Short sale being professionally negotiated by Anchor Legal Group, PLLC.  More pictures of the interior coming soon.  The “Approved Short-Sale Price” is the price that the bank approves the property to be sold, not the listing price.  All the seller’s property is to be removed from the property prior to the final walkthrough.  Short-sale does not mean investor only or cash only. It means there’s a process.  The seller is motivated.
